Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:42.04,text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水潭之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:43.76,text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水潭之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:47.27,text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水潭之中别有天地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.30,0:23:49.15,text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水草
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.48,0:23:51.04,text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水仙花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.47,0:23:54.90,text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在有萤火虫引路的森林深处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:57.61,text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被笛声所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.49,0:24:00.92,text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与那个可爱的女孩相会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.68,0:24:04.12,text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀着谢意
